description.narrative:
Green, secure, sustainable workplace for effective delivery on targeted SDGs and the development objectives by key UN organizations.
Establishing and maintaining a safe, modern and environmentally friendly workplace, where key UN organizations, working to promote the economic and social development in developing countries, get optimal conditions and utilize synergies for effective and cost efficient delivery on their individually targeted SDGs and specific development objectives in line with the on-going reforms of the UN Development System.
FL §06.36.01.14 The UN House in Copenhagen
